Subject: [PATCH v5 18/20] memstick/r592: convert r592_io kthread into kthread worker API
Date: Mon, 22 Feb 2016 15:57:08 +0100
Message-Id: <1456153030-12400-19-git-send-email-pmladek@suse.com>
In-Reply-To: <1456153030-12400-1-git-send-email-pmladek@suse.com>
